articles.contents:
About Me
Hi, my name is Tejas Mundhe and I am an incoming freshman at Walnut Hills High School. I enjoy playing soccer and swimming as well as having a passion for computer science where I have coded in Javascript Python, and R.
About this Project
This project was made through Kaneâ€™s Free High School Data Science Bootcamp to explore how different states were affected by the Covid-19 Pandemic. The data set for this project was from a Covid 19 Vaccines and Deaths by State Dataset in which the data was gathered directly from the CDC.
Goals
To Visualize the Covid-19 Deaths for every U.S state
Learn about making plots and websites that are available on the internet
Take my first steps into the world of data science
